timing_report...worstcase_mode(25.10)    timing_report...worstcase_mode(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_arrival_property_worstcase_mode

Syntax
       timing_report_arrival_property_worstcase_mode <integer>

       Default: 0

       Differentiates the clock and data phases based on the arrival_* proper-
       ties  (see  get_property command) . The accepted values are 0, 1, 2, or
       3.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

